applicantId       string   uuid assigned by the platform
firstName         string
lastName          string
dateOfBirth       yyyy-mm-dd
address           object   {street, city, state, zip, country}
documentType      enum     [PASSPORT, ID_CARD, DRIVERS_LICENSE]
frontImage        binary   jpeg/png <= 10 MB
backImage         binary   optional
selfieImage       binary   optional
level             string   “basic” | “enhanced” (AML+PEP+Sanctions)